<CORRECTION>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
George Brett of the Kansas City Royals still owns his famous "pine tar" bat. It 
was erroneously reported in Monday's editions that the bat was owned by a 
collector. Brett occasionally lends the bat to the Baseball Hall of Fame in 
Cooperstown, N.Y., where it is displayed. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
