<HEADLINE>
<P>
JOYNER NAMED ANGEL OF WEEK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Wally Joyner, who had three game-winning hits and one game-winning run batted 
in on a walk last week, is The Times' Orange County Edition Angel of the Week. 
</P>
<P>
Joyner had two home runs and nine RBIs during the week and batted .448 with 13 
hits in 29 at-bats. 
</P>
<P>
The Times will donate $200 in Joyner's name to the Boys and Girls Clubs of 
Orange County. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
JOYNER, WALLY; BASEBALL PLAYERS; HONORS; CALIFORNIA ANGELS (BASEBALL TEAM) 
</P>
